ten span several seconds.\n\nNow let’s look at the third way to control haptics: **Emphasis Points**.\n\n\n<img width=\"100%\" src=\"media://./assets/continuous.png\" />\n/newpage\n\nAn **Emphasis Point** is a brief, crisp haptic feedback lasting only a few tenths of a second, creating a short, sharp sensation.\n\nEmphasis points appear as blue vertical bars on the amplitude envelope.\n\nTo add emphasis points, use the Emphasis tool, accessible from the Tool Bar or by pressing the shortcut E.\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n<video width=\"100%\" src=\"media://assets/addemphasis.mp4\" autoplay loop/>\n\n\nTake a moment to feel these 3 emphasis points.\n","lastUpdate":1750685562716,"haptic":{"version":{"major":1,"minor":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"editor":"Haptic Studio","source":"Silence.wav","project":"Silence","tags":[],"description":""},"signals":{"continuous":{"envelopes":{"amplitude":[{"time":0,"amplitude":0.00007626055},{"time":0.2021901357515007,"amplitude":0,"emphasis":{"amplitude":1,"frequency":0.5}},{"time":1.0004846835330992,"amplitude":0,"emphasis":{"amplitude":1,"frequency":0.5}},{"time":1.8047998739825526,"amplitude":0,"emphasis":{"amplitude":1,"frequency":0.5}},{"time":2,"amplitude":0.000117901014}],"frequency":[{"time":0,"frequency":0},{"time":2.01,"frequency":0}]}}}}},{"clipId":"0dd475ef-d94d-4999-bb8f-569128eb34a7","name":"Intensity","audioAsset":{"filename":"Silence.wav","path":"Silence.wav","channels":1},"waveform":{"envelope":[{"time":0.005011338,"amplitude":0.00013438895},{"time":0.01,"amplitude":0.000117552176},{"time":0.015011338,"amplitude":0.00012362152},{"time":0.02,"amplitude":0.00013327246},{"time":0.025011338,"amplitude":0.0001582209},{"time":0.03,"amplitude":0.00013651904},{"time":0.035011336,"amplitude":0.00014479263},{"time":0.04,"amplitude":0.00014195681},{"time":0.045011338,"amplitude":0.00013723127},{"time":0.05,"amplitude":0.000120788},{"time":0.055011336,"amplitude":0.00015957771},{"time":0.06,"amplitude":0.00021543364},{"time":0.06501134